    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an unrivaled example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a commitment to preservation. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly 'mint' specimen. Performance is as seamless as its aesthetic, ensuring a driving experience that mirrors its original factory delivery.",
