      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled environment and driven only on fair-weather weekends. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections; it has been treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating to ensure long-term protection. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free of any creasing or wear, and even retains that signature new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the premium audio system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, and I have a complete, organized binder of every receipt and inspection report since new. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion or road debris. This is a collector-grade specimen that needs nothing but a new garage. Included in the sale are two original keys, the factory window sticker, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
